海外新增峰值或尚未到来；NBA无限期停赛；德国再拦瑞士医疗物资文|《财经》数据研究员 徐进 图|《财经》视觉中心 编辑|郝洲一、国内防疫成果显著，对输入病例已布下天罗地网图1今日国内简述：国内3月10日报告累计确诊病例80793例，新增15例。
New peaks may not yet arrive; the NBA is suspended indefinitely; Germany has re-routed Swiss medical equipment & # 160; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & nbsp; & nbsp;
国内非湖北地区境外输入病例6例，青岛本地病例1例。
There were 6 cases imported from outside Hubei area and 1 case from Qingdao.
湖北非武汉地区连续7日零新增。
Hubei non-Wuhan area added 7 consecutive days.
武汉新增病例首次降至个位数。
Wuhan new cases fell to single digits for the first time.
河南境外输入病例来自意大利，3月7日8:50抵达首都机场后，转乘大巴、高铁于当日21:50到达郑州，步行回家；3月10日8时被警方和社区人员以大数据追踪到而转送集中隔离点，后发热转至医院，11日确诊；截至11日12时，已初步通过流调判定其密接者24人，并已集中隔离；该患者有隐瞒境外旅居史情节，警方以涉嫌妨害传染病防治罪立案调查。
On March 7, 2008, after arriving at the Capital Airport at 8: 50 a.m., Henan Province was transferred to Zhengzhou by bus and high-speed rail at 21: 50 on the same day.
青岛本地病例3月10日发热就诊，11日检测确诊；现已对其13名密接者集中隔离，进一步追踪仍在进行。
Qingdao local case March 10 fever clinic, 11 test confirmed; its 13 informants have been concentrated in isolation, further tracking is still ongoing.
总的感觉就是，国内追踪、隔离、检测、救治能力已经得到大大提升，除了铜墙铁壁、天罗地网，在资源能力上和病毒的关系已经从疫情暴发初期10个指头要应对成百上千个跳蚤，转为现在100个指头应对1个跳蚤。
The general feeling is that domestic tracking, isolation, detection and treatment capabilities have been greatly enhanced, with the relationship between resource capacity and the virus having shifted from 10 fingers to hundreds of fleas in the early stages of the outbreak to 100 fingers to 1 flea at present.
病毒已经很难在国内再掀波澜。
The virus has made it hard to turn the tide at home.
人们越来越关注返岗复工，恢复正常生活。
There is growing concern about returning to work and returning to normal life.
而国外现在正在重复中国疫情早期阶段，迅速从10个指头应对1个跳蚤转为10个指头需要面对成百上千个跳蚤。
And foreign countries are now repeating the early stages of the epidemic in China, where a flea switch from 10 fingers to 10 fingers is facing hundreds of fleas.
刹车似乎来得有点晚。
The brakes seem a little late.
二、世卫最终承认新冠疫情全球“大流行”图2境外新增病例已超过7000，继续呈加速状态，但根据中国的疫情初期增长曲线判断，峰值尚未到来。
The World Health Organization (WHO) has finally acknowledged that the number of new cases outside the territory of the New Crown Epidemic chart 2 has exceeded 7,000, continuing to accelerate, but judging by China's initial growth curve, the peak is yet to come.
日内瓦时间3月11日傍晚，世界卫生组织正式宣布，新冠疫情的暴发已经构成全球性“大流行”。
On the evening of March 11, Geneva time, the World Health Organization officially announced that the outbreak of the new crown epidemic has become a global "pandemic."
世卫组织总干事谭德塞说：“我们以前从未见过冠状病毒引发的大流行。
"We have never seen a coronavirus-induced pandemic before," said WHO Director-General Theresa Tupper.
我们以前也从未见过得到控制的大流行。
We have never seen a controlled pandemic before.
” 此前，历史公认为全球“大流行”的流行病有：14世纪的黑死病、19世纪末的天花、1918年的西班牙流感、1981年的艾滋病毒和2009年的H1N1疫情。
Previous global pandemics have been widely recognized as such: the 14th century Black Death, smallpox in the late 19th century, the Spanish flu in 1918, HIV in 1981 and H1N1 in 2009.
图3欧洲的单日新增较前一日翻倍。
Figure 3 Europe's one-day increase doubles from the previous day.
德国总理默克尔与德国卫生部长延斯·施潘（Jens Spahn）3月10在议会党团会议上均发出警告示，如果不能率先开发出且使用疫苗，那么60%至70%的德国人可能会被感染新冠病毒。
German Chancellor Angela Merkel and German Health Minister Jens Spahn warned at a parliamentary caucus meeting on March 10 that 60% to 70% of Germans could be infected with the new crown virus if they are not the first to develop and use the vaccine.
三、美国仅剩7个州未报告感染病例图4由于疫情的恶化，美国24个州以及首都华盛顿都已宣布进入紧急状态。
Figures 4. Twenty-four states and the capital, Washington, have declared a state of emergency as the epidemic worsens.
仅剩7个州未报告感染病例。
Only seven states remain unreported.
当地时间3月11日晚，美国总统特朗普在全国电视讲话中表示，受疫情影响，自13日起的30天内，将暂停“从欧洲到美国的所有旅行”，但英国除外。
In a nationally televised speech on the night of March 11, US President Trump said the outbreak would suspend "all travel from Europe to the United States" for 30 days from 13 days, with the exception of the United Kingdom.
此外，有消息称，总统特朗普有意将本次疫情列为国家灾难，届时可以启动“斯塔福德灾害救援和紧急援助法”（Stafford Disaster Relief and Emergency Assistance Act），为联邦政府拨出最多400亿美元作为紧急抗疫资金。
Moreover, it has been reported that President Trump intends to classify the outbreak as a national disaster, when the Stafford Disaster Relief and Emergency Assistance Act can be activated, allocating up to $40 billion to the federal government to fund an emergency response.
63岁的著名影星汤姆・汉克斯（Tom Hanks）3月11日通过社交媒体表示，他与妻子丽塔（Rita Wilson）在澳大利亚感染了新冠肺炎。
Tom Hanks, a 63-year-old film star, told social media on March 11 that he and his wife Rita Wilson had contracted pneumonia in Australia.
此外，犹他爵士队的中锋戈贝尔被检测出感染新冠病毒后，NBA表示将暂停全部比赛，直至另行通知。
In addition, the NBA said it would suspend all competition until further notice after Utah center Robert Goebbels was found to be infected with the new crown virus.
四、欧洲呼吁各国在抗疫方面加强合作、保持团结图5不断加重的疫情压得欧洲喘不过气来。
Europe Calls on Nations to Enhance Co-operation in the Fight Against the Epidemic and Maintain Solidarity Chart 5 The growing epidemic is overwhelming Europe.
继前几日拦截瑞士的口罩之后，德国汉堡海关又扣押了一个瑞士进口商从中国订购的装有手术手套的货运集装箱。
Following the interception of a Swiss mask a few days earlier, Hamburg, Germany, seized a cargo container containing surgical gloves ordered from China by a Swiss importer.
图6意大利新增病例再一次打破纪录，首次突破2000。
Fig. 6 Italy's new cases break records again, breaking 2000 for the first time.
病死率达到6.6%。
The fatality rate reached 6.6 per cent.
意大利总理孔特3月11日宣布将抗疫措施再升级，下令国内的所有店铺，除超级市场、食品店及药房之外，全部必须关闭，但餐厅仍可维持外卖服务，公司的员工食堂如能保证客户之间的距离至少有1米，则仍可继续开放。
Prime Minister Conte announced on 11 March that the epidemic would be further escalated by ordering all shops in the country, except supermarkets, food stores and pharmacies, to be closed, but the canteen would remain open if it guaranteed at least one metre of distance between customers.
企业亦必须关闭除对生产必要以外的所有部门。
Enterprises are also required to close all sectors except those necessary for production.
3月11日，中国红十字会组织的抗疫专家组启程前往意大利，并携带相关人道救援物资，支援意大利共同抗击新冠肺炎疫情。
March 11, the Chinese Red Cross organized a team of anti-epidemic experts to Italy, and with the relevant humanitarian supplies, Italy to support the fight against the new crown pneumonia.
五、韩国警惕疫情反弹，开始严防输入病例图7韩国中央灾难安全对策本部3月12日表示，15日零时起，从法国、德国、西班牙、英国、荷兰5个国家来韩的旅客必须接受强化的检疫程序。
South Korean tourists from five countries -- France, Germany, Spain, the United Kingdom and the Netherlands -- must undergo enhanced quarantine procedures at 0000 hours, the ministry said Wednesday.
在过去的一周里，法国、德国、西班牙等国家的确诊患者人数激增5~10倍，韩国政府担心会出现从这几个国家的新冠肺炎重新输入病例，所以制定了相关对策。
In the past week, the number of patients diagnosed in countries like France, Germany, and Spain has soared by a factor of 5-10, and South Korea's government, fearful of a new influx of cases from these countries, has devised a response.
从欧洲出发在14日内经由迪拜和莫斯科进入韩国的人也要经过特别入境程序。
Persons entering Korea within 14 days from Europe via Dubai and Moscow are also subject to special entry procedures.
六、伊朗又有三名高官确诊，供氧和通风设备紧缺图8目前，伊朗疫情最严重的地区仍是首都德黑兰，以及周边的马赞德兰省和库姆省，三个地区分别已确诊2370例、918例和804例病例，占比45.5%。
Diagnosis is made by three more high-ranking Iranian officials: Shortage of Oxygen Supply and Ventilation Fig. 8 Currently, Tehran, the capital city, and the surrounding provinces of Mazandran and Qom continue to be the hardest hit, with 2,370, 918 and 804 cases, respectively, diagnosed in the three regions, accounting for 45.5%.
为加大对确诊病例和疑似病例的收治能力，伊朗开始借鉴中国经验，疫情严重的多个省份宣布征用展览中心、停工工厂等场地建设临时“方舱医院”。
In order to increase the capacity to treat confirmed and suspected cases, Iran has started to learn from China's experience, and several provinces with severe epidemics have announced the construction of temporary "square-cabin hospitals" at venues such as exhibition centers and shut-down factories.
伊朗再有三名高官确认感染新冠肺炎，分别为伊朗第一副总统贾汉吉里（Eshaq Jahangiri）、文化遗产、旅游和手工业部部长穆内桑（Ali Asghar Mounesan）和工业矿业贸易部部长拉赫马尼（Reza Rahmani）。
Three more senior Iranian officials confirmed the infection, namely First Vice President Eshaq Jahangiri, Minister of Cultural Heritage, Tourism, and Handicrafts Ali Asghar Mounesan, and Minister of Industry, Mines, and Trade Reza Rahmani.
3月11日，世卫组织又向伊朗提供了4万套测试盒，但供氧和通风设备仍旧紧缺。
On 11 March, WHO provided an additional 40,000 test kits to Iran, but oxygen and ventilation are still in short supply.
【特别说明：以上统计，2月28日前为世卫组织官方统计数据，数据截止时间为北京时间每日17时；从2月28日开始，数据由《财经》根据公开资料统计，截止时间为北京时间每日9时】七、全球疫情数字速览：1、【105亿欧元做空】欧洲疫情持续爆发，做空者开始瞄准欧洲市场，桥水基金成为做空领头羊，做空37家欧洲公司，包括联合利华、SAP、法国巴黎银行、道达尔、阿迪达斯、达能。
The figures are due at 17: 00 daily Beijing time from Feb. 28, according to Caijing daily data. Since Feb. 28, data from Caijing has been closing at 9: 00pm daily according to open data.
按照周一收盘价计，桥水做空的头寸金额总和105亿欧元（折合118亿美元）。
The bridge shorted positions totalled 10.5 billion euros ($11.8 billion) at Monday's closing price.
在此情况下，欧洲央行行长拉加德发出警告，现在需要采取紧急措施，由于新冠疫情的冲击，欧洲可能会遭遇与2008年全球金融危机类似的重大经济风险。
In this context, ECB President Christine Lagarde has warned that urgent measures are needed now that Europe could face significant economic risks similar to those of the 2008 global financial crisis, owing to the impact of the new crown epidemic.
2、【5天内搬离宿舍】美国媒体3月11日报道，哈佛大学发言人瑞切尔·丹（Rachael Dane）在一封邮件中表示，为“减少我们社区的人口密度”，该校要求学生在3月15日前搬出宿舍。
Harvard University spokesman Rachael Dane said in an e-mail that students were required to move out of their dormitories by March 15 to "reduce the population density in our community."
此前，哈佛大学校长巴科（Lawrence Bacow）已宣布，由于新冠病毒疫情影响，该校将在3月23日前逐步过渡到网上授课。
Earlier, Lawrence Bacow, Harvard's president, had announced that the school would gradually transition to online teaching by March 23 because of the new crown virus.
小结：湖北非武汉地区连续7日零新增。
Summary: Hubei non-Wuhan region on the 7th consecutive day added zero.
武汉新增病例首次降至个位数。
Wuhan new cases fell to single digits for the first time.
世界卫生组织正式宣布新冠疫情构成“全球大流行”；意大利进一步升级管控措施。
The World Health Organization officially declared the new crown as a "global pandemic"; Italy further upgraded its controls.
美国仅剩7个州未报告感染病例，接下来，该好好说说美国了。
There are only seven states in the United States that have not reported infections, and now it's time to talk about the United States.
